text: Rao Jamil Akhtar was elected as Okara Tehsil nazim in 2005 unopposed. He was member Provincial Assembly of the Punjab with Rao Sikandar Iqbal. Then again contested in 2013 which he lost. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Pakistani politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
